{"tid":414220,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"facebook 一年賺既以億計你班on9又唔嘈?","createTime":"2017-09-26T05:10:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-26T06:30:53.000Z","uid":37264,"like":17,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"f7d8956418acc3732d96057fd8abb5ffc52f648f","tid":414220,"uid":37264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T05:10:57.000Z","msg":"唔係話支持連狗<br />\n但係而家又唔係攞支槍指住你個頭迫你買<br />\n又有得比你諗買咩plan<br />\n個價位又唔係咩過份數字<br />\n你係唔鐘意既大把巴打提供左alternative solution比你地remove ad<br />\n有曬上中下策咁仲嘈咩呢?<br />\n成班乞衣妄想人地比免費野你比一世"},{"pid":"31c7b9bd068dee5ce416bddfc68cfe8646eaf790","tid":414220,"uid":21423,"like":7,"dislike":4,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T05:24:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"31d0fa5a27311a6889a6d221b1d85310b835fb2a","tid":414220,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T05:26:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/26/131609_9c3e1b49383a64961018638a7f90d0dc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F26%2F131609_9c3e1b49383a64961018638a7f90d0dc.jpg&h=1f9af891&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ae2866050848de23f393aedc89ac29a22d868123","tid":414220,"uid":29270,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T05:32:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>FB冇陰濕廣告，冇全版廣告，冇彈出廣告，冇月費計劃。重有FB又唔係forum，嘈咗你都唔知啦，你都冇朋友。</blockquote><br />\n你直頭冇上過Facebook添啦屌<br />\n<br />\n首頁每隔幾個Post就有一條「贊助」<br />\n直頭係廣告商出既貼文黎，可以大張圖又長文，咁都唔叫陰濕廣告？<br />\n<br />\n仲未計PC板，右邊幾格，乜野推薦社群、乜野推薦專頁<br />\n全部都廣告黎，不過經過調整，口味會比較合乎用戶<br />\n<br />\n週圍捉錯字捉到你傻撚左<br />\n要講廣告，Facebook根本可以認一哥添啦屌"},{"pid":"be74dc61ef4fa47328ce8efb2e9e041ec46f5c5e","tid":414220,"uid":74935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T05:33:09.000Z","msg":"出面屌到以為要比錢先上得黎"},{"pid":"afd92408d86d7d1de2df4fad79c081f9e8ffd265","tid":414220,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T05:33:38.000Z","msg":"幾時有人話要免費<br />\n$15 hkg+ vip唔見有人屌？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a12b306599939ad206b6c7323dbe2a715a62999d","tid":414220,"uid":6124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T05:35:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾時有人話要免費<br />\n$15 hkg+ vip唔見有人屌？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nhkg+? Server? Cost?"},{"pid":"c1ba339a4b0e3e30c7fca2687a7cafb17690b4dc","tid":414220,"uid":29270,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T05:36:29.000Z","msg":"反連登唔緊要，幫Facebook辯護真係癡撚左<br />\n<br />\n大把人講緊個Feed系統改到七彩<br />\nfollow左都未必追到post，要比錢要確保人地收到你新post<br />\n<br />\nYoutube都搞緊類似既野<br />\n仲未計巴哈、香討等等老牌討論大把商業元素<br />\n<br />\n個個大網站都搞緊商業化，不過唔係直接用廣告咁去賺錢<br />\n<br />\n唔係話鬥慘，不過連登都算好喇屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50e6b7aca3962be61f98d9dc8049926a0e76339f","tid":414220,"uid":49992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T05:36:50.000Z","msg":"因為有5毛同叫人返高登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有位入唔入又唔洗成本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18c841bf09ec40762fbde887a218e3815f98c8b6","tid":414220,"uid":126293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T05:36:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>FB冇陰濕廣告，冇全版廣告，冇彈出廣告，冇月費計劃。重有FB又唔係forum，嘈咗你都唔知啦，你都冇朋友。</blockquote><br />\nfacebook D 廣告行銷方式多到可以有 facebook marketing strategy 啊肥屍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36e7cec292a2a962cf29f265473ec75bb3bdaf59","tid":414220,"uid":119494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T05:37:26.000Z","msg":"無限支持 就算要比1000我都會比 當支持香港人言論自由<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{