re":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T06:06:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ae15afb2df669e97b7816cd803b25e694b442f35","tid":414220,"uid":126293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T06:09:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>FB冇陰濕廣告，冇全版廣告，冇彈出廣告，冇月費計劃。重有FB又唔係forum，嘈咗你都唔知啦，你都冇朋友。</blockquote><br />\nfacebook D 廣告行銷方式多到可以有 facebook marketing strategy 啊肥屍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同我講嘅陰濕，全版，彈出有咩關係？<br />\n成班傻撚理解能力有問題就咪死出嚟啦</blockquote><br />\n原來你..<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc7a9fd2543bdd6a13d15e9016aaae9837442631","tid":414220,"uid":37733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T06:12:19.000Z","msg":"fb值喎<br />\n抵佢賺<br />\n連狗個抄返黎既forum點值188呀"},{"pid":"e738f0bd86b2e4bbf465b2bcff5306d2cd39e7a5","tid":414220,"uid":15249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T06:30:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>fb值喎<br />\n抵佢賺<br />\n連狗個抄返黎既forum點值188呀</blockquote><br />\n走啦咁"}]}